' 5.08 mouse_up
' ============================================================================
' MOUSEUP.LST
'
' Use this procedure to ensure program execution is delayed until both mouse
' buttons have been released.
' ============================================================================
'
PROCEDURE mouse_up
  ' *** Waits for user to release mouse buttons
  LOCAL mx%,my%,mk
  REPEAT
    MOUSE mx%,my%,mk
  UNTIL mk=0
RETURN
